1c;","facilityInfoList":[{"facilityItemList":[{"itemCode":5,"itemName":"Note(s)","itemValue":"Universal Studios Japan has two ATMs (Mitsubishi UFJ Bank and AEON Bank). The AEON ATM is located in the Darkroom (inside the cinema), while the Mitsubishi UFJ Bank ATM is on the left side of the entrance (inside the cinema)."}]}]},{"facilityName":"Souvenir shop","facilityCode":"18","iconUrl":"\u0026#xf0125;","facilityInfoList":[{"facilityItemList":[{"itemCode":5,"itemName":"Note(s)","itemValue":"Tax-Free Service  \nService Details: Shopping at stores within the park is tax-free. (Excludes some carts, etc.)  \nAvailable for foreign visitors staying less than 6 months  \nPassport required  \nYour total purchase amount must exceed the eligible threshold.  \nJapanese web services are not supported.  \nTax-Free Counter: Studio Gift West (2:00 PM–)  \nTotal sales for tax-free \"consumable goods\": ¥5,000–¥500,000 (tax-excluded)  \nTotal sales for tax-free \"general goods\": ¥5,000 or more (tax-excluded, excluding consumables)  \nA 3.3% processing fee applies to tax-free items (as of September 1, 2023)."}]}]},{"facilityName":"Accessibility","facilityCode":"27","iconUrl":"\u0026#xf1527;","facilityInfoList":[{"facilityItemList":[{"itemCode":5,"itemName":"Note(s)","itemValue":"1. Restrooms  \nService details  \nMale/female/wheelchair accessible, nursing bed available  \nLocation: Various areas, table service restaurants, Stage 33™  \n\n2. Wheelchair rental  \nService details  \nMade of stainless steel with hand brakes.  \nApproximate dimensions: Backrest 100 x height (floor to seat) 44 x width 64 (cm)  \n\n*Limited quantity. No reservations accepted.  \n*Service details and prices are subject to change without notice.  \nPrice: ¥500 per unit (tax-free)  \nLocation: Counter on the right after entering."}]}]}]}}}]},{"templateType":"recommandations","templateName":"Recommended","iconShow":false,"moduleList":[{"moduleType":"tripmoments","moduleName":"tripmoments","tripMomentModule":{"to